Jukebox Kiosk Mode setup

create the folder ~/.config/autostart

copy the kiosk.desktop file to the ~/.config/autostart

Open the Raspberry PI configuration app and ensure that

	System->Desktop Auto Login is on 
	System->Console Auto Login is on 

 edit /etc/lightdm/lightdm.conf 

        ensure autologin-user is set to the target user. 



